  "detailed_description": "<strong>Whimsy</strong> is the story of a girl who has always lived in the forest.<br>One morning she awakes to find little red footprints outside her door.<br>As any fearless protagonist would, she follows them. They lead her through the forest where she meets new woodland friends (and foes) while solving charming puzzles.<br><br>my name is madison karrh and i made this lil macabre game. thank you for playing something another human made.<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>interesting forest creatures<br></li><li>puzzles on puzzles on puzzles<br></li><li>sweet tiny tunes crafted for you by Diamond Anaya</li></ul>",
